.TH ffs 3 2024-05-02 "Linux man-pages (unreleased)"
.SH NAME
ffs, ffsl, ffsll \- find first bit set in a word
.SH LIBRARY
Standard C library
.RI ( libc ", " \-lc )
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #include <strings.h>
.P
.BI "int ffs(int " i );
.BI "int ffsl(long " i );
.BI "int ffsll(long long " i );
.fi
.P
.RS -4
Feature Test Macro Requirements for glibc (see
.BR feature_test_macros (7)):
